{"tid":230523,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"啲韓國佬真係冇乜禮貌","createTime":"2017-05-05T12:09:35.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-05T12:15:53.000Z","uid":22197,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"85165ba82c0b9c6936e13dee12743e221889e396","tid":230523,"uid":22197,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-05T12:09:35.000Z","msg":"今日同男朋友上晴空塔<br />\n排緊隊搭𨋢上去<br />\n之後有條死韓佬拆鳩人地啲圍欄行入去打尖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n咁我就企係度唔郁特撚登唔比佢打尖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n佢就逼鳩入黎 然後我繼續唔郁 <br />\n佢就比我撞撚到 <br />\n跟住行到去前面就搵埋條韓國整容雞一齊望鳩我<br />\n係咁擰轉頭望<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n之後望鳩返佢又即係擰轉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n咁撚柒就唔好出國啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 第一次覺得韓國佬咁乞人憎"},{"pid":"02bf9aee8888cbd8cf138a506b3d78944379cdfe","tid":230523,"uid":98645,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-05T12:15:53.000Z","msg":"其實韓國人嘅質素同蝗差唔多<br />\n大大聲、推推撞撞之類一樣"}]}